For this assignment i have introduced an arbitrary max projectile count
It is currently set to 5 but to change it you cna just alter the variable in the main file

TO play, shoot the spider with a fireball by pressing space
You can only move by useing the left or right arrow or a and d

Each time the spider reaches the end of the top half, you lose a life
whenever you lose all three lives, the game ends and the window automatically closes.